	      <td colspan="2">
		<P><!---->The Haskell-Beginners mailing list is for the discussion of primarily beginner-level topics related to the Haskell language.  Feel free to ask beginner-level questions, or to discuss beginner-level topics, related to Haskell here.<br><br>Please don't cross-post to both Haskell and Haskell-Beginners.<!----></P>
	  <p> To see the collection of prior postings to the list,
	      visit the <a href="http://www.haskell.org/pipermail/beginners/">Haskell-Beginners
		  Archives</a>.
	      
	  </p>
	</TD>
      </TR>
